<p><span style="font-weight: bold;">Upwork top rated badge.  Hi Upwork Team I Recently Get Top Rated Badge but Upwork did not reduce my fee its still 20% and also did not get other benefits We and selected third parties use cookies or similar technologies for technical purposes, to enhance site navigation, analyze site usage, assist in our marketing efforts, and for other purposes as specified in … I checked and it seems that your 12-months earnings are not yet $1,000.  The count is updated every Saturday.  These … Cassie Moorhead Jun 20, 2023 | 16 Min Read Work &amp; Career Article As a freelancer, your reputation is everything.  As an Amazon affiliate partner we … djondinium Community Manager In response to mohammedimran90 09-29-2021 03:28 AM Sep 29, 2021 03:28:07 AM by Aleksandar D Hi Mohammed, Yes, you're … Benefits of Top Rated Status.  However, regardless if you have the badge or not, the fees will slide to 10% and 5% once you pass an earning threshold.  So if you’re just starting out on UpWork, keep that in mind.  New to Upwork 101.  I have 13 out of 16 weeks on my states page.  Customized Job Digest emails highlighting top Oct 8, 2020 09:28:23 AM by Petra R.  *The 30 free Connects are valued at about $4.  Building an … Upon checking, it looks like you do not currently have a 100% complete profile, which is part of the criteria for earning the badge.  Also, my &quot;Top Rated eligible weeks&quot; is decreasing every week, it came down to 13 from 16.  Post Reply Latest Articles DevOps Engineering: The Future of IT Industry for Experienced and Fresh Professionals.  One of the must have qualifications that you still need to … 01-09-2023 03:54 AM.  7 An account in good standing.  Hi, my top rated badge has dissapeard from &quot;My stats&quot; for some reason, although my top-rated eligiblity is 16 by 16, and I've earned over a 1000 in the last 12 … Once all requirements are met you will receive the Top Rated badge automatically.  09-09-2022 07:42 PM.  Warning che